_International" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_International" target="_blank">news</a> about Tom McCabeâHe was very good to me over the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Millennium" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Millennium" target="_blank">years</a> and will be missed greatlyâMy <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thought" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thought" target="_blank">thoughts</a> and <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prayer" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prayer" target="_blank">prayers</a> are with his familyâNicola Sturgeon also paid tribute to Mr McCabeThe <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Minister" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Minister" target="_blank">First Minister</a> tweeted âVery <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiromani_Akali_Dal" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiromani_Akali_Dal" target="_blank">sad</a> to hear of the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">death</a> of former <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Labour_Party" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Labour_Party" target="_blank">Labour</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament" target="_blank">MSP</a> Tom McCabeâHe was a genuinely <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hero" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hero" target="_blank">good guy</a> My <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thought" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thought" target="_blank">thoughts</a> are with his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wife" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wife" target="_blank">wife</a> and <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family" target="_blank">family</a>âSix <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Millennium" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Millennium" target="_blank">years</a> ago McCabe'